rue\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oww1665702974971.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oww1665702974971.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oww1665702974971.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"oww1665702974971\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      TXT Connector Options\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"oww1665702974971__txt_connector_options_177166\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can assign connector options by setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$TXT_PARAMS</span> in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"oww1665702974971__topic_d61688e1_d61689e1_d61690e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oww1665702974971__p_d61691e1_d61692e1_d61693e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$TXT_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uni</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">bom</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oww1665702974971__topic_d40777e1_d40778e1_d40779e1_d40780e1_d40781e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d90732e93\">\n                        \n Options\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oww1665702974971__li_d27074e1_d27075e1_d27076e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zcj1665702779599.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zcj1665702779599.html\" title=\"Connector option that defines the default Unicode encoding used by the TXT connector. The encoding for a specific entity can be specified using the /uni switch in an entity-to-connector assignment.\">uni</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oww1665702974971__li_d27077e1_d27078e1_d27079e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bqi1665702975044.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bqi1665702975044.html\" title=\"Connector option that determines whether a Byte Order Mark (BOM) is required in Unicode files accessed by the TXT connector. The behavior for a specific entity can be specified using the /bom switch in an entity-to-connector assignment.\">bom</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oww1665702974971__topic_d40782e1_d40783e1_d40784e1_d40785e1_d40786e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d90732e128\">\n                        Syntax Rules</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oww1665702974971__p_d61700e1_d61701e1_d61702e1\">The syntax rules for setting connector options\n\t\tare:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oww1665702974971__li_d27080e1_d27081e1_d27082e1\">Options can be set using either a colon (<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>) or an equals sign (<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>). Thus\n\t\t\t <var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var> is the same as\n\t\t\t <var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>. <p class=\"p\" id=\"oww1665702974971__p_d61703e1_d61704e1_d61705e1\">For example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">ri:on</code> and\n\t\t\t <code class=\"ph codeph\">ri=on</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oww1665702974971__li_d27083e1_d27084e1_d27085e1\">The total length of the assignment should not\n\t\t\t exceed 80 characters. Use the short format shown in the example for multiple options.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oww1665702974971__li_d27086e1_d27087e1_d27088e1\">Each option must be specified only once </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oww1665702974971__li_d27089e1_d27090e1_d27091e1\">Multiple options must be separated by commas\n\t\t\t (<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>) </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oww1665702974971__li_d27092e1_d27093e1_d27094e1\">Words and numbers within each option are\n\t\t\t separated by one or more spaces or tabs </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oww1665702974971__li_d27095e1_d27096e1_d27097e1\">Options are not case-dependent </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530781\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530781\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "TXT Connector Options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 TXT Connector Options You can assign connector options by setting USYS$TXT_PARAMS in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file. USYS$TXT_PARAMS = uni = Value { , bom = Value } Options uni bom Syntax Rules The syntax rules for setting connector options are: Options can be set using either a colon ( : ) or an equals sign ( = ). Thus Option : Value is the same as Option = Value . For example: ri:on and ri=on . The total length of the assignment should not exceed 80 characters. Use the short format shown in the example for multiple options. Each option must be specified only once Multiple options must be separated by commas ( , ) Words and numbers within each option are separated by one or more spaces or tabs Options are not case-dependent Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}